PoC:
Path:	../sysop/
File:	RTE_popup_file_atch.asp
NOTE: 	To upload an asp web shell inject a filename with for example ...  shell.asp;1.jpg


Risk:
=====
The security risk of the remote file upload vulnerability is estimated as high.


